# hilavitkutin-extensions

Contract-bound extension host layer over `hilavitkutin-linking`. Owns
descriptor shape, pull-based discovery, lifecycle orchestration, and
capability dispatch. Domain-agnostic: knows about descriptors and
capabilities, not about any specific domain like NAM or diagnostics.

`#![no_std]`, no allocator, no dyn. Downstream consumer contract crates
layer their domain-specific types on top. The sibling proc-macro crate
`hilavitkutin-extensions-macros` emits the repr-C descriptor and
trampolines on the extension author's behalf.
